esian Community Shield]]'''</center>\n|<center>'''1'''</center>\n|<center>0</center>\n|<center>[[2013 Indonesian Community Shield|2013]]</center>\n|\n|-\n|<center>'''Piala Galatama''' </center> \n|<center>'''1'''</center>\n|<center>0</center>\n|<center>1992<ref>{{cite web|title=Indonesia&nbsp;\u2013 List of Cup Winners|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesi/indocuphist.html|accessdate=1 December 2014|language=Indonesian}}</ref></center>\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n=== AFC (Asian competitions) ===\n*'''[[Asian Cup Winners' Cup]]'''\n** [[1993\u201394 Asian Cup Winners' Cup|1993-94]] \u2013 Quarter-finals\n*'''[[AFC Cup]]'''\n** [[2013 AFC Cup|2013]] \u2013  Quarter-finals\n\n==Season-by-season records==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n! Season\n! League/Division\n! Tms.\n! Pos.\n![[Piala Indonesia]]\n!colspan=2|[[Asian Football Confederation|AFC]] competition(s)\n|-\n|[[1994\u201395 Liga Indonesia Premier Division|1994\u201395]]\n|Premier Division\n|34\n|'''5 in West Div.'''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|-\n|[[1995\u201396 Liga Indonesia Premier Division|1995\u201396]]\n|Premier Division\n|31\n|'''9 in West Div.'''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|-\n|[[1996\u201397 Liga Indonesia Premier Division|1996\u201397]]\n|Premier Division\n|33\n|'''7 in West Div.'''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|-\n|[[1997\u201398 Liga Indonesia Premier Division|1997\u201398]]\n|Premier Division\n|31\n|''Did not finish''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|-\n|[[1998\u201399 Liga Indonesia Premier Division|1998\u201399]]\n|Premier Division\n|28\n|'''Second round'''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|-\n|[[1999\u20132000 Liga Indonesia Premier Division|1999\u201300]]\n|Premier Division\n|28\n|'''6 in West Div.'''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|-\n|[[2001 Liga Indonesia Premier Division|2001]]\n|Premier Division\n|28\n|'''7 in West Div.'''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|-\n|[[2002 Liga Indonesia Premier Division|2002]]\n|Premier Division\n|24\n|'''Semi-final'''\n|\u2013\n|\u2013\n|\u